    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> spicy Cape Malay-style basa curry</strong> with the <strong>yellow sultana rice</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled</strong> <strong>chilli cucumber </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>chilli rounds</strong> over the top (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
